@startuml sequence_auth_flow
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Authentication Flow - OAuth2 PKCE

actor User
participant "Angular SPA" as SPA
participant "Entra ID" as Entra
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Web API" as API
database "SQL DB" as DB

User -> SPA: Access protected page
SPA -> SPA: Check for valid token
SPA -> Entra: Redirect to /authorize\n(code_challenge, scope)
Entra -> User: Show login form
User -> Entra: Enter credentials + MFA
Entra -> SPA: Redirect with auth code
SPA -> Entra: POST /token\n(code + code_verifier)
Entra --> SPA: ID token + Access token
SPA -> SPA: Store tokens in memory
SPA -> GW: GET /api/v1/me\n(Bearer token)
GW -> GW: Rate limit check
GW -> API: Forward request
API -> API: Validate JWT signature\n(JWKS endpoint)
API -> API: Extract claims:\nuserId, email, roles, orgId
API -> DB: Upsert user record\n(first login provisioning)
DB --> API: User record
API --> GW: 200 OK + user profile
GW --> SPA: User profile JSON
SPA --> User: Render dashboard

@enduml
